  "title": "Mathematics Tuition Teacher",
  "description": "<p><strong>About Axiom Education</strong></p>\n<p>Axiom Education is a <strong>leading</strong> tuition centre for IB, A-Level (H2), Integrated Program (IP) and O-Level. We pair rigorous, structured teaching with a fun, competitive classroom vibe. With proven materials, engaging methods and a <strong>vibrant, high-energy learning community</strong>, our students consistently climb to 7s and As.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>The Role</strong></p>\n<p>Teach O level, IP, IB &amp; H2 <strong>Mathematics </strong>full-time. Run interactive, exam-focused classes and mentor students</p>\n<p>Ideal for an educator with <strong>3–5 years’</strong> strong results.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What You’ll Do</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Deliver engaging lessons aligned to O Level, IP, IB &amp; H2 Mathematics syllabus</li>\n  <li>Create notes, practice sets, and model answers; track progress with clear feedback.</li>\n  <li>Coach exam technique (timed practice, structured problem-solving, marking criteria).</li>\n  <li>Support students beyond class with mentorship and guidance.</li>\n  <li>Stay current with syllabus updates and exam trends.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What You Bring</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>3–5 years</strong> proven IB/H2 teaching or tutoring experience in <strong>Mathematics </strong>with strong outcomes.</li>\n  <li>Degree in <strong>Mathematics, Engineering</strong> or related field.</li>\n  <li>Mastery of core topics and problem-solving strategies.</li>\n  <li>Clear communicator; organised, proactive, high-energy, student-centric.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Compensation (Full-Time)</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Revenue-share on Net Class Fees </strong>with significant upside as your classes scale.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Work Location</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Holland Village</li>\n  <li>Balmoral Plaza</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Apply Now</strong></p>\n<p>Send your resume to info@axiomeducation.sg</p>",
